data.description: Welcome Home to the ASHLAND PARK NEIGHBORHOOD- Hanover County's best kept secret! NEW PAINT, NEW CARPET, and has been Professionally Cleaned - It is Move in Ready for it's lucky new Owners! This charming 1744 sf, 3BR+2.5BA Craftsman home is situated on an oversized, cul-de-sac lot. Hardwood floors throughout the first floor, and  plenty of natural light. First level features a spacious Family Room with gas burning fireplace and hardwood floors, as well as an eat in kitchen with stainless appliances, pantry storage and bar seating. Just off the kitchen you have a good size laundry room and private half bath. Second floor opens up to a loft area - which is perfect for that home office, and also includes 2 secondary bedrooms and a full hall bathroom. Off the loft you will find French doors opening up to the primary bedroom suite with walk-in closet, bathroom with double vanity, and low step in shower stall. Rear deck overlooks the large backyard that also backs up to the neighborhood's walking trails. Upgrades include NEW HVAC 2020, replaced back deck 2020, crawl space encapsulated and conditioned! This is the one you have been waiting for!
